article_title: Emily Bazar: Taxed by Obamacare tax forms? Here’s some help
article_text:
Millions of Californians will receive Obamacare-related tax forms for the first time

Spot an error in the form? You need to get it corrected, but it’s going to take some effort

article_metadata.title: Emily Bazar: Taxed by Obamacare tax forms? Here’s some help | Fresno Bee

og.description: Millions of Californians will receive Obamacare-related tax forms this year for the first time – if they haven’t already – including some 13 million who had Medi-Cal coverage in 2015.
